casebody.data:
Amr MOHSEN, petitioner,
v.
UNITED STATES. No. 13-8958. Supreme Court of the United States March 31, 2014.

Motion of petitioner for reconsideration of order denying leave to proceed in forma pauperis denied, and petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Ninth Circuit dismissed. See Rule 39.8.
